entries.femaleVariant: Michelle! Michelle, you here...? Michelle, say something! Please!
They didn't do a thing. They couldn't have. Your kidneys are acting up... Whatta they need sick kidneys for?
Don't... This isn't a joke, all right? Say something... Anything.
I can find you that way... And we'll go home.
I'll take ya to the movies like you wanted. Your choice! Just please... say something!
